:0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:49:33.000Z","msg":"我夠唔明點解楊呢d垃圾都會有咁多fans添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事實係佢真係拎左嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10f401a2184f7743089d4f5fcf972ab87b30e43","tid":810300,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:50:42.000Z","msg":"4大？唔覺喎"},{"pid":"b507d238e7b791f5ab404dc60eb805b18dbdab93","tid":810300,"uid":171901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成就一定楊最高啦<br />\n多其他人一個影后</blockquote><br />\n楊係我見過最聲色藝不全又上到位嘅藝人<br />\n同汪阿姐一撚樣"},{"pid":"a58bc75199c7bdb96fec3ee872628a47b407efc0","tid":810300,"uid":199692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:57:53.000Z","msg":"搞錯呀，吳若希，菊梓喬唔係天后"},{"pid":"0742d0df0381e148b715b5996eb79fb1961de47f","tid":810300,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3de564fcb47c6472433361ab37dab5f33e6295af","tid":810300,"uid":132587,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"4f2074cdbde5c408527ef559e1103cfaf62eb0e2","tid":810300,"uid":9217,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:33:48.000Z","msg":"成就一定楊最高啦<br />\n多其他人一個影后"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:36:33.000Z","msg":"志明與春嬌套垃圾野拎影后都拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:18:56.000Z","msg":"鄭秀文拎過未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f249294abe42464fd8aa23650461925a5ad362e","tid":810300,"uid":206987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a58bc75199c7bdb96fec3ee872628a47b407efc0","tid":810300,"uid":199692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:57:53.000Z","msg":"搞錯呀，吳若希，菊梓喬唔係天后"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:20:15.000Z","msg":"憑啲咩"},{"pid":"d64b978377c0ce64d2c803fa21d8fecbc20f944f","tid":810300,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:43:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zfe588qM5zU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dzfe588qM5zU&d=NcR7R2YgvSmy%2FZlfdaZChUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=797c9920\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zfe588qM5zU</a><br />\n<br />\n作為一個歌手，要得到的，全部得過了，還可以有甚麼不滿足？她又居然不惜工本為新歌製作MV。動員70多位演員，全盛時期的《火熱動感La La La》，大概也沒有如此規模。首新歌，還是一首廣東歌。<br />\n<br />\n「我見很多人得閒便踩一踩廣東歌，話廣東歌快死，新一代的聽眾全部只聽外國歌。可否不要一味放棄？可否用其他方法扶持一下？聽聞現在一個MV，幾萬元便要完事，好慘，導演已經不知道還可以怎樣拍。我是帶住使命去做事。刻意做大一點，讓其他人知道有人還在做，廣東歌要死，也不會死得太快。」<br />\n<br />\n鄭秀文說過，現時每做一件事，也注重出發點。全個行業，恐怕剩下鄭秀文一個有熱誠得來又有足夠牙力，可以說服公司投放資源的。「意義是超越鄭秀文拍一個大家喜歡的MV，而是要看看這個MV如何為廣東歌出點綿力。先要喚醒大家願意再度關注，如果觀眾連留心也不肯留心，廣東歌做得再好也沒有用。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507184c38e66a5c591acba50fb17143055ba6429","tid":810300,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b507d238e7b791f5ab404dc60eb805b18dbdab93","tid":810300,"uid":171901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成就一定楊最高啦<br />\n多其他人一個影后</blockquote><br />\n楊係我見過最聲色藝不全又上到位嘅藝人<br />\n同汪阿姐一撚樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"運氣好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7458f1876b4bdd01b24ccedc841e0f04f758ddb3","tid":810300,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11d88bcde60f3bd346ace7d10fec2160a05d4b40","tid":810300,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c39a6d53600c50fc43d687e72389371eb67b5c37","tid":810300,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7a4e800f00b68a5183179ba506b0cf9881ce7897","tid":810300,"uid":132587,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:35:13.000Z","msg":"鄭秀文<br />\n歌影視全部有代表作<br />\n佢同joey係四個